SignalR resources:
    https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/signalr/introduction?view=aspnetcore-3.1

VS Code keyboard shortcuts:
    Ctrl-Shift-P    - command pallette

To merge a branch back into the main (develop) branch:
- Check everything in to the sub-branch
- Switch to the develop branch
- Use Ctrl-Shift-P to select Merge Branch, and select the sub-branch you want to bring in
- Use Ctrl-Shift-G (source control view) to help resolve on any resulting conflicts 

To see which elements of the game- or player-state JSON is used by the client:
- See /client/src/redux/slices/game.js or hub.js